citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 10:45 on 3/29/23.
Phone calls were made to both numbers on file and voice mail messages were left because the gates were closed to the
county park the facility is located within. Emails were also sent to both the director and animal curator with no response
during the 30 minutes the inspector waited.
End Section
